<title>USA: VLSI names Bala Iyer CFO.</title>
<headline>VLSI names Bala Iyer CFO.</headline>
<dateline>SAN JOSE, Calif. 1997-01-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>VLSI Technology Inc said it named Bala Iyer vice president and chief financial officer. He succeeds Gregory Hinckley, who resigned to become chief operating officer and chief financial officer of Mentor Graphics Corp.</p>
<p>Iyer had been vice president and controller of VLSI since joining the company in 1993. He has worked in the semiconductor industry for over 15 years.</p>
